metadata.name: The Light Of Happiness
metadata.description:
When we were young, My father always asked, 'What do you want to be when you grow up?' But I'm the only one who doesn't have an answer. I just need to focus on studying hard to get a good job, but it makes me feel pressured and unhappy, and when I get to know the world of NFT, I know it will make me happy.

3280 x 4720 px
